2007-10-01  Emmanuele Bassi  <ebassi@openedhand.com>

	* clutter/clutter-fixed.h: Add CLUTTER_FIXED_TO_INT() and
	deprecate CLUTTER_FIXED_INT(), for symmetry with
	CLUTTER_FIXED_FROM_INT().

