2007-01-19  Tomas Frydrych  <tf@openedhand.com>

	* clutter/clutter-fixed.c: (clutter_sqrti):
	Use union instead of casting int <-> float to get rid of
	punned-pointer warning and avoid gcc optimatisation breaking
	the function on arm.

